    "question": "If $x = \\frac{2}{2+\\sqrt{3}}$, then $\\sqrt{x} + \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x}} = ...$ (TSTET 2017)\n$x = \\frac{2}{2+\\sqrt{3}}$ అయితే, $\\sqrt{x} + \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x}} = ...$",
